<SYNC Start=3449785><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3452190><P Class=KRCC>
끝까지 해라
<SYNC Start=3453623><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3454959><P Class=KRCC>
